### ========================================
### GDPR - Article 17: Right to Erasure (Right to be Forgotten)
### ========================================

### IMPORTANT: Create a test customer first before anonymizing
### Run this to create a test customer for anonymization

### 63. Create Test Customer for Anonymization - Alice Test
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "alice.test@example.com",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "phoneNumber": "555-1111"
}

### 64. Create Order for Alice (To test that orders remain after anonymization)
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customerEmail": "alice.test@example.com",
  "totalAmount": 99.99,
  "shippingAddress": "123 Test St"
}

### 65. Grant Consent for Alice (To test consent tracking)
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com/consents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consentType": "Marketing",
  "consentVersion": "1.0"
}

### 66. Verify Alice's Data Before Anonymization
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 67. Export Alice's Data Before Anonymization (For comparison)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 68. Anonymize Customer - Alice Test (GDPR Article 17 - Right to be Forgotten)
### This will:
### - Soft delete the customer (IsDeleted = true)
### - Anonymize: FirstName, LastName, Email, PhoneNumber
### - Keep orders intact (referential integrity)
### - Record deletion reason and timestamp
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com/anonymize?reason=Customer requested account deletion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 69. Verify Alice's Data After Anonymization (Should return 404 or anonymized data)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 70. Try to Anonymize Again (Should return 400 - already deleted)
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/alice.test@example.com/anonymize?reason=Duplicate request
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 71. Anonymize Customer - Not Found (Should return 404)
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/nonexistent@example.com/anonymize?reason=Test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 72. Anonymize Customer - Default Reason
POST {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/customers/bob.johnson@example.com/anonymize
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


